---
title: Creamy Aubergine Curry with Mushrooms, Lentils and Potatoes
description: Meaty in texture, and mild in flavour, the mighty aubergine is the hero ingredient in this creamy vegetarian curry. Seasoned with our delicious North Indian spice blend and packed with juicy mushrooms, potatoes and protein-packed lentils, this is a dish that will nourish you from the inside out. Top with a good handful of freshly chopped coriander, a good squeeze of lime and you’re good to go. A real weeknight winner.
